snippet.title: Dinkum - Official Announcement Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Dinkum is an adorable and wholesome farming sim with an Australian twist, coming to Steam Early Access on July 14th.

Named for the Australian slang word for "authentic," Dinkum joins the likes of Stardew Valley, Harvest Moon, and Story of Seasons in wholesome farming fun. Build your farm, raise animals, meet townsfolk, and face dangers at nighttime with your buddies. Fair Dinkum!

#IGN #IGNExpo
